data.description: Motivated Seller! Only selling due to work transfer. Check out this gorgeous 2 bedroom plus den 2 bath home in gorgeous Bonavie Cove neighborhood. This community does not have a CDD! Enter through the gates of this great neighborhood passing the gorgeous lake view clubhouse with pool, grill, patio, firepit and exercise room! This home has Faux wood plank tile floors, quartz countertops in kitchen as well as the bathrooms. A great flex/den room right off the kitchen works great as a office or even a guest bedroom. Enjoy the great sunsets from the screened in Leni. Just a short walk to the dog park, the pond and the clubhouse. Get in now to see this home! It has a whole home kenetico water softner system and when we get those great south florida hurricanes no need to worry! this system does not require electricity to run, enjoy your soft water showers and great drinking water even when power is out! Keep your car safe in the amazing garage with  the epoxied floor and overhead storage this place will keep you organized.
